imdb.plot outline: Roommates Sarah Williams (from Jim Henson's Labyrinth) and Christine Daae (from Phantom of the Opera) find out that they're living in the same building as Jareth (Labyrinth) and Erik (Phantom). Stalking, magic, and hijinks ensue in this audio web series of the comic created by Rebecca Morse. Based on an idea by Ashe Rhyder, art and story by Rebecca Morse.
